## §0 Terminal goal — 11-verb space substrate (4 그룹 모두 working spec)

hexa-space 도착지 = **11-verb space substrate (core·engineering·observation·life) 모두 working spec + 1+ verb 실증 데이터 cross-link (SpaceX/NASA/ISS public)**.

DoD:
1. `core` (cosmic + starship) 통합 spec.
2. `engineering` (aerospace + transport + engineering + systems) Falcon 9 / Starship public data fit.
3. `observation` (astrodynamics + astronomy + obs_astronomy) Gaia DR3 cross-verify.
4. `life` (astrobiology + medicine) ISS public health data n=6 fit.

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | Space projection |
|--------|-------|------|------------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12-month launch window cadence |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | 4 mission phases (design / build / launch / operate) |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | crewed / uncrewed |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech | 24-hour orbit harmonic (LEO ~ 90 min × σ·τ/2) |

